@@TJvDragDrop.TargetStrings
Summary
  Receives the names of dropped files.
Description
  Use TargetStrings to assign a TStrings descendant that will automatically receive the names of the
  files dropped on the drop target. For example:
  
  <CODE>
  JvDragDrop1.TargetStrings := ListBox1.Items; </CODE>
  When files are dropped on the drop target, the list box will be filled with a list of the names of
  the dropped files.
See Also
  TJvDragDrop.DropTarget, TJvDragDrop.OnDrop

